quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  36,51,Futhi liyoshawa icilongo kulapho bona beyophuma emathuneni beshesha bebheke eNkosini yabo
  36,52,"Bayothi, “Oh usizi kuthina! Ngubani lowo osivuse endaweni yethu, lokhu kuyilokhu onomusa akwethembisa nezithunywa zakhuluma iqiniso”"
  36,53,Angeke kube yilutho ngaphandle kokukhala okukodwa kulapho bona bonke beyolethwa ngaphambili kwethu
  36,54,Ngakho-ke ngalolusuku umphefumulo angeke wenziwe okungenabo ubulungiswa ngalutho futhi angeke ninikwe umvuzo ngaphandle kwaloko enanikwenza
  36,55,Ngempela izihlali zesivande kulolosuku ziyobamatasatasa ngezinto eziyinjabulo
  36,56,"Bona kanye namakhosikazi abo bayoba semthunzini, bacambalale endaweni ephakeme"
  36,57,Okwabo lapho phakathi yizithelo futhi okwabo kuyoba yinoma ngabe yini abayicelayo
  36,58,Ukuthula! Izwi elivela eNkosini enesihawu
  36,59,Futhi hlukanani namuhla Oh nina eniyizoni
  36,60,Angizange yini nginiphoqe Oh bantwana ba-Adam! Ukuthi ningamkhonzi usathane? Ngempela yena uyisitha senu esigqamile
  36,61,Nokuthi nikhonze mina? Lena yindlela elungile
  36,62,Futhi ngempela wadukisa iqembu elikhulu phakathi kwenu ngakube naningenawo yini umqondo
  36,63,Lesi yisihogo enanethenjiswe sona
  36,64,Ngenani kusona namhlanje ngenxa yokuthi naningakholwa
  36,65,Kulolusuku siyayisicilela imilomo yabo futhi izandla zabo zizokhuluma nezinyawo zabo zizofakaza mayelana naloko ababekusebenzela
  36,66,Futhi ukube besithanda besizosusa amehlo abo bese beyaphuphutheka endleleni bese bebona kanjani
  36,67,Futhi ukube besithanda besizobaguqula ezindaweni zabo bebengeke besakwazi ukuya phambili nokuphindela emumva